      "content": "idk, i dont know if i want to fight it. it just feels so heavy, u know? like the character is just tired of existing in a world that's literally deleting them. everything is just gonna be gone anyway. if they just stop fighting and let the void take them, isn't that just... more peaceful? it feels way more real than some grand heroic struggle.",
